Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似漫長  實則轉瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至今日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖杯戰爭 參加的魔術師共有七人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們被稱為Master
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,役使分為七個職階的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為爭奪獨一無二的聖杯而展開的廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若也是魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必早有覺悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛宮士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為那種荒唐的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就輕易的把人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的將是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝身繫於吾之側
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾命化為汝之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如遵從聖杯之意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如遵從此意此理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則應我召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝 身負三大言靈之人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從抑制之輪前來此地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天平之守護者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能成為正義的夥伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是你召喚出的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能不是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am the bone of my sword
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵從召喚前來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的Master嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我為了士郎辛苦求來的海報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可抗力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來話長…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拽名詞來敷衍我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家才不上當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 我要洗點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借前輩用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心慣壞了士郎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時都是他慣著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啐 年輕人跑去卿卿我我了嗎 去死吧